thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Daniel & Peter

author: Daniel & Peter
title: Daniel & Peter
text:
Kirsty Eldridge was our property manager for the last twelve months. My partner and I want to recognise how fantastic Kirsty was to us as landlords and also to the tenants. We would like to nominate Kirsty for property manager of the year for Kirsty's professionalism and common sense approach to problem solving.
Kind regards
Dan Salvador and Peter Wilson
0426 998 009
